{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "第二回\"怒箭\"：沙漠中，卫天鹏率两名劲装少年发现濒死的小方。卫天鹏以水和肉为筹码试探小方，随后突然向一旁装死的白袍人射出怒箭，却被对方两指轻松夹住。卫天鹏认出此人正是江湖中最神秘的卜鹰（卜大公子）。二人因三十万两黄金劫案产生交锋——铁翼护送的黄金被劫，卫天鹏怀疑卜鹰是劫匪，卜鹰坦然承认是为了黄金而来，但二人争论黄金是否已被运走。小方在旁观察并参与讨论，展现出冷静机智的性格。章末卫天鹏亮出杀机，怒箭与斩鬼刀蓄势待发。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我叫卫天鹏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "看来你一定已经在沙漠中行走了很多天，一定也遇上了那场风暴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这两天你有没有看到过什么可疑的人。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "看到过一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "遇到可疑的人，我只有一种法子对付他。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "你是不是会先割掉他一只鼻子，削掉他一只耳朵，逼问他的来历，然后再一刀杀了他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在你是不是还要说自己是个可疑的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "我说不说都一样，像我这样的人如果还不可疑，还有谁可疑？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你想要我用这种法子对付你？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "反正我已经快死了，随便你用什么法子对付都没关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "但是你可以不必死的，只要有半壶水，一块肉，就能救活你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我有水，也有肉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你为什么不求我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "我为什么要求你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "你若肯救我，用不着我求你，你若不肯，我求你也没有用。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们知道他是谁？凭你们也敢在他面前拔刀。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "但是你若以为你躺在地上装死就可以让我认不出你，你也错了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "你认得他？他是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "他就是卜鹰！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到今天我总算见到了卜鹰。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我也想不到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "你跟他有仇。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "你为什么要杀他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我只不过要试试他究竟是不是卜鹰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "如果他是卜鹰，就绝不会死在你的箭下，如果他死了，就绝不会是卜鹰。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "如果他死了，死的只不过是个无足轻重的人，'怒箭神弓斩鬼刀'纵横江湖，杀错个把人有什么关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "一点关系都没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "为了三十万两黄金，就算杀错三五百个人也没关系。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "三十万两黄金，哪里来的三十万两黄金？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我只知道黄金是从哪里来的，却不知道到哪里去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "你是不是认为他知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "卜大公子是千金之体，若不是为了三十万两黄金，怎么会到这既无醇酒，也没有美人的穷荒僻壤来？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "卜大公子挥手千金，视钱财如粪土，若不是因为常常有这种外快，哪里来的这许多黄金让他挥手散去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "只有一点不太对。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "哪一点。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "三十万两黄金究竟有多少？我也不知道，我从来都没有看过这么多的金子，我只知道就算有人肯把这三十万两黄金送给我，我也绝对搬不走的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "你认为这位卜大公子一个人就能把三十万两黄金搬走！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你怎么知道他是一个人？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "我确实是为了这件事来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "我的开销一向很大，这点金子我正好用得着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "是三十万两，不是一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "的确不是一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "所以这批黄金无论落在谁手，要把它藏起来都很难。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_ying",
      "speaker_name": "卜鹰",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "的确很难。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "既然没法子藏起来，就绝对没法子运走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_bu_ying",
      "text": "所以我看你不如还是把它交出来的好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "就算他是为了这件事来的，这批黄金也未必已落在他手里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "护送这批黄金的人是铁翼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "text": "铁胆神枪铁翼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_tian_peng",
      "speaker_name": "卫天鹏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "江湖中能杀他的人有几个？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    }
  ],
